OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with variable cloud
OL,6,Ffor most. Some sunny spells are
OL,7,Flikely, with temperatures near normal
OL,8,Ffor March, however a brisk breeze will
OL,9,Flead to it feeling cooler. A few
OL,10,Fshowers will also move into northern
OL,11,Fand western parts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud thickening through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight. Winds also
OL,15,Fstrengthening, with upland gales
OL,16,Flikely, and perhaps some rain for a
OL,17,Ftime. Staying mild, and frost free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
